where <m:math><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mi>ρ</m:mi></m:mrow></m:mrow></m:math> is the density of the medium in which the sound wave travels and <m:math><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mi>v</m:mi><m:mn>w</m:mn></m:msub></m:mrow></m:mrow></m:math> is the speed of sound in the medium.</para></item>
        <item id="import-auto-id1448826"><para id="eip-id1168466596301">Sound intensity level in units of decibels (dB) is
